Plan: Restructure Daily HTML Files into archives/{yyyy}/{mm}/

 Context

 The workspace root is becoming cluttered as daily diary files accumulate. Moving them into
 a monthly archive hierarchy (archives/2026/03/) keeps the root clean and scales naturally
 as months and years are added. Since this is a pure static site opened via file:// (no
 server, no build step), all path fixes must use relative ../../../ traversal — not
 absolute or root-relative paths.

 ---
 Depth arithmetic (fixed for all future dates)

 root/                     ← index.html, styles.css, favicon.svg live here
   archives/               [1 level]
     {yyyy}/               [2 levels]
       {mm}/               [3 levels]
         {yyyy-mm-dd}.html ← always 3 levels deep → root = ../../../
 ../../../ is stable for every future month and year.

 ---
